  "title": "Assistant Marketing Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job purpose</strong></p><p>1.        Support the Brand Manager to develop and execute integrated e-commerce and marketing strategies <br />           that drive growth and achieve business objectives. </p><p>2.        Lead planning and implementation of online campaigns and promotional mechanics across platforms <br />           such as TikTok, company website, and departmental stores e-commerce sites.</p><p>3.        Oversee visual merchandising for all online channels to ensure brand consistency and impact. </p><p>4.        Champion data-driven decision-making by leveraging advanced analytics to optimize performance and<br />           guide strategic initiatives.</p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><p>·            Bachelor’s Degree in Business, Marketing, or related field.</p><p>·            Minimum 5 years of experience in the beauty industry; e-commerce experience preferred.</p><p>·            Strong analytical skills with proven experience in data visualization, reporting, and business intelligence <br />             tools (e.g., Salesforce, Power BI, Tableau).</p><p>·            Excellent communication skills.</p><p>·            Highly organized, proactive, and able to manage multiple priorities independently.</p>",
